With the launch of [Salt](https://salt.bountysource.com/), Bountysource is
[competing](https://github.com/gratipay/inside.gratipay.com/issues/316)
directly with us for the open-source market. How do we compare, feature-wise?

## Things They Have and We Don't

If you're coming here from [Gratipay or
Bountysource](http://gratipay-or-bountysource.guide), welcome! Feel free to +1
the features you care the most about:

- [bounties](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/issues/214) :)
- [one-time payments](http://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/issues/5)
- [updates](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/issues/2521)
- [tagging](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/issues/3127)
- [funding goals with progress bars](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/issues/3057)
- [social sharing links](https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com/issues/3)

What else?
